Para uso nas requisições, colocar a palavrar Bearer mais um espaço e o access_token Bearer <access_token>

Exemplo

Bearer eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCIgOiAiSldUIiwia2lkIiA6ICIzLWtDQlRpcTI1b0hkYW1NS1kxT1YwZ1RpOWRGMTg2ZDFvakljcW1rTWVNIn0..Dqoo3VP9BRMt7mszpqETtcumlUhG1O-vljnMpOSn4XJQVXPpP85kLleE5ppsgaFsIq4hWvHGU-hiSWYmKBXthGT1EsAi2l8AyoRgYTML0deo_KMElhl8SaQb7iFJbK3aAN1PJGShM0jTMSKeTKtoyUw4IQPfXk4rdvDlxIHgbSd7LdSSb_HEMEcJsOo0R-myd3W9uIK9DUCrrtKmJ9AOTb2LQgKlhiwzML678_W6CdI_aVpZ22FUfcv29gmGGvr8CMHVf0Uvxovpou0s6TaP6_tu7VqkswJaeqM4_SFi3KeEfGhaPmcV3ivcCdr1VWBIugWx9KDAT-P9VZ1-z6F5Ow

Bearer

